message: Rule applicable: mod_to_bubble ([("Bubble", 6000)]), to expression: 8 % a, resulting in: {SafeMod(8,a) @ (a != 0)}
Rule applicable: bubble_up ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: (2 = {SafeMod(8,a) @ (a != 0)}), resulting in: {(2 = SafeMod(8,a)) @ And([(a != 0)])}
Rule applicable: expand_bubble ([("Bubble", 8900)]), to expression: {(2 = SafeMod(8,a)) @ And([(a != 0)])}, resulting in: And([(2 = SafeMod(8,a)), And([(a != 0)])])
Rule applicable: introduce_modeq ([("Minion", 4200)]), to expression: (2 = SafeMod(8,a)), resulting in: ModEq(8, a, 2)
Rule applicable: remove_unit_vector_and ([("Base", 8800)]), to expression: And([(a != 0)]), resulting in: (a != 0)
